## Quick comparison: what differs across platforms

| Attribute | ACP (file upload) | Google Merchant Center | Meta |
|---|---|---|---|
| ID field name | `item_id` | `id` | `id` |
| Title field name | `title` | `title` | `title` |
| Image field name | `image_url` | `image_link` | `image_link` |
| Product URL field | `url` | `link` | `link` |
| Price format | `"29.99 USD"` | `"29.99 USD"` | `"29.99 USD"` |
| In-stock value | `in_stock` | `in_stock` | `in stock` |
| Variant group field | `group_id` | `item_group_id` | `item_group_id` |
| Condition required? | optional | required if used/refurbished | always required |
| Brand required? | yes | yes (most categories) | yes |
| Checkout enablement | `is_eligible_checkout: true` | UCP profile + checkout API | Meta Commerce Manager |
